{"title":"农家少妇速写","authors":["方小亢"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":7,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农家少妇速写"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方小亢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吻过小女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎起头巾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁天色微明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着露水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕山行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕山行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕山行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山路长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶在晌午以前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要砍柴一担；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南山有玉米半亩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施肥莫误农家谚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着担，爬南山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗珠滴到了脚底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老鹰飞到了村西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村西放出了一窝小鸡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是鸡埘还没有做起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但见那老鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总在飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总在飞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽高忽低，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽高忽低……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}